ated films]]\n[[Category:English-language films]]\n[[Category:The Flintstones]]\n[[Category:Yogi Bear]]\n[[Category:Scooby-Doo]]\n[[Category:The Jetsons]]\n[[Category:The Banana Splits]]\n[[Category:1970s educational films]]\n[[Category:1980s educational films]]\n", "name_user": "Moe1810", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eFilmstrips", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hanna-Barbera_Educational_Filmstrips"}
